      <div class="c-group-header has-image ">
  
    <a href="https://www.polygon.com/what-to-watch"><img src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23218913/jbareham_220131_ecl1049_what_to_watch.png" alt="What to Watch"></a>
  
  <h1 class="p-page-title ">What to Watch</h1>
  
    <p class="c-group-header__desc">Your time is precious, and your options are endless. The good news: We watch it all so you don’t have to. Polygon’s What to Watch highlights the best, the funniest, the scariest, and the most exciting in movies, TV, and everything in between. Stop scrolling, start watching!</p>
  
  
  
  
